             was indicted for <rs id="t18080217-94-off544" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080217-94-off544" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080217-94-off544" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080217-94-cd545" type="crimeDate">19th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-94-off544 t18080217-94-cd545"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-94-off546 t18080217-94-cd545"></join>, a bag, value 14 d. a leather strap, value 1 d. two pecks of horse beans, clover chaff, and grains, mixed together, value 7 d.
            </rs> and 
               
                  <persName id="t18080217-94-defend838" type="defendantName">
