                     <interp inst="t18080217-94-off546" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving them, knowing them to have been stolen
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18080217-94-person839">
                  JOHN 
                  FRITH
               <interp inst="t18080217-94-person839" type="surname" value="FRITH"></interp>
