                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-94-defend836 t18080217-94-punish551"></join>
               Fined One Shilling and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>WEST, <rs id="t18080217-94-verdict552" type="verdictDescription">
